tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_communication_sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    session_start_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    session_end_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    session_duration INTERVAL,
    participant_1_name VARCHAR,
    participant_1_role VARCHAR,
    participant_2_name VARCHAR,
    participant_2_role VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE session_metadata (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_date TIMESTAMP,
    quantum_protocol VARCHAR(50),
    session_duration INTERVAL,
    session_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE session_participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    participant_name VARCHAR(50),
    participant_role VARCHAR(20),
    participant_contact VARCHAR(100),
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES session_metadata(session_id)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_communication_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    participant1_id INT,
    participant2_id INT,
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_communication_sessions (
 session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 session_start TIMESTAMP,
 session_end TIMESTAMP,
 communication_protocol VARCHAR(50),
 session_status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE communication_partners (
 partner_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 partner_name VARCHAR(100),
 partner_location VARCHAR(100),
 partner_contact VARCHAR(50),
 partner_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE communication_messages (
 message_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 session_id UUID,
 sender_id UUID,
 receiver_id UUID,
 message_content TEXT,
 message_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE communication_logs (
 log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 session_id UUID,
 log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
 log_type VARCHAR(50),
 log_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    start_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    end_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    quantum_protocol VARCHAR(50),
    encryption_key VARCHAR(100),
    session_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_messages (
    message_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id UUID,
    sender_id UUID,
    receiver_id UUID,
    message_text TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_errors (
    error_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id UUID,
    error_type VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);
